nodes.text: Skeck Draggle was the first mate of the Drunk Dancer. He belonged to the same six-fingered, lanky, severe-faced humanoid species as Archyr Beil.

He was the first to meet Roan Shryne and Olee Starstone when they first met. He, along with Archyr Beil accompanied
Shryne when the party went to Alderaan in order to smuggle former senator Fang Zar off the planet.
